title: Khatarnak Kannada Movie (2013)
description: The film is about a serial rapist and killer. The story begins with a group of young psychology students going in search of his life to understand why he became a savage. At the same time, the heroine has a similar attack by an unknown person like the one the serial killer does. The students pick up stories from the village Gowda, the investigation officer and others who are involved in investigation and arrest of the serial killer Umesh. They learn that he has done crimes one more brutal than the other. As their chilling journey continues, the heroine has to confront Umesh in the end. Was it Umesh himself who had attacked her and is she seeking revenge on him? There is an interesting twist to the question.
